summary: Phidata is a comprehensive framework designed to create advanced multi-modal agents that integrate memory, knowledge, tools, and reasoning capabilities. This framework allows developers to build teams of agents that work together, enabling complex problem-solving and interactive user communication via a user-friendly Agent UI. With built-in features such as multi-agent orchestration, structured outputs, and monitoring capabilities, Phidata provides a streamlined environment for developing and managing intelligent agents across various applications.
